<li>Vincent Duclert,2006,"Alfred Dreyfus",Librairie Artheme Fayard,<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/2213627959" class="internal">ISBN 2 21362795 9</a></li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=George_R._Whyte&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="George R. Whyte (page does not exist)">George R. Whyte</a>, <i>The Dreyfus affair&#160;: a chronological history</i>, Basingstoke 2008</li>
</ul>
<p><a name="Newspaper_Articles" id="Newspaper_Articles"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Dreyfus_affair&amp;action=edit&amp;section=17" title="Edit section: Newspaper Articles">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Newspaper Articles</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Adam Kirsch (July 11, 2006), <a href="http://www.nysun.com/article/35780" class="external text" title="http://www.nysun.com/article/35780" rel="nofollow">The Most Shameful of Stains</a>, <i>The New York Sun</i></li>
<li>Stanley Meisler (July 9, 2006), <a href="http://www.latimes.com/news/opinion/sunday/commentary/la-op-meisler9jul09,0,6805861.story?coll=la-sunday-commentary" class="external text" title="http://www.latimes.com/news/opinion/sunday/commentary/la-op-meisler9jul09,0,6805861.story?coll=la-sunday-commentary" rel="nofollow">Not just a Jew in a French jail</a>, <i>The Los Angeles Times</i></li>
<li>Ronald Schechter (July 7, 2006), <a href="http://www.forward.com/articles/the-ghosts-of-alfred-dreyfus/" class="external text" title="http://www.forward.com/articles/the-ghosts-of-alfred-dreyfus/" rel="nofollow">The Ghosts of Alfred Dreyfus</a>, <i>The Forward</i></li>
<li>Kim Willsher (June 27, 2006), <a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/france/story/0,,1807241,00.html" class="external text" title="http://www.guardian.co.uk/france/story/0,,1807241,00.html" rel="nofollow">Calls for Dreyfus to be buried in Panthéon</a>, <i>The Guardian</i></li>
</ul>
